    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Weird viscous residue floats in this oily potion, and it bears one of the most horrendous smells you have ever come across, however, when ingested it bares no taste. When consumed, slowly for the next hour you start to understand some of the words that are spoken to you in any language, not all, just enough for you to understand the overall underlying intent of the implied message. This does not affect the written text. If you attempt to speak back towards the creature that is speaking to you, what you say is always erroneous just enough to cause either confusion, anger, or belief that the user is sick and needs to be urgently hospitalized.</p>",
